full_text: Prince Harry and Meghan, the Duchess of Sussex, on Sunday announced the birth of their second child, Lilibet Diana. Her name is a tribute to Queen Elizabeth II's childhood nickname and the late Princess Diana. https://t.co/oSZVUADbU9
